Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.12,0:01:31.72,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What's wrong?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.72,0:01:34.05,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Something came up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.49,0:01:38.39,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Saki?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.39,0:01:39.79,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Later.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.79,0:01:41.39,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Takizawa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.65,0:02:03.02,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs20\fe0\b0\i0\c&Hffffff&\fnPalatino}Episode 10:\NWho Killed Akira Takizawa?{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.39,0:02:10.16,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why didn't Takky get on the train?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.16,0:02:12.03,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I don't know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.89,0:02:13.03,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs20\fe0\b0\i0\c&Hffffff&\fnPalatino}Inbox{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.03,0:02:14.82,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs20\fe0\b0\i0\c&Hffffff&\fnPalatino}Osugi\NBe careful!\NI have to tell you\Nsomething important\Nabout Takizawa.{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.36,0:02:19.03,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs20\fe0\b0\i0\c&Hffffff&\fnPalatino}Osugi\NFW: Be careful!\NLook at the data on\NTakizawa I uploaded\Nto the Eden site!\NHe's using aliases.{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.76,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs20\fe0\b0\i0\c&Hffffff&\fnPalatino}Osugi\NFW: Be careful!\NI found proof in Toyosu\Nthat Takizawa was\Ninvolved in the\Ndisappearance of the\N20,000 NEETs. Please\Nget away from him right\Naway if you can.\NBe careful!{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.92,0:02:37.09,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Are you the one who called me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.09,0:02:39.09,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm Daiju Mononobe.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.09,0:02:42.12,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I hear you want to punch out Mr. Outside.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.12,0:02:44.43,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Did you get your memory back?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.43,0:02:47.10,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Wait, did you talk to ltazu?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.10,0:02:51.37,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes. He called you a hero.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.37,0:02:53.90,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I wonder if you can continue\Nliving up to those expectations.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.90,0:02:55.44,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"Continue"?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.46,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What expectations?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.31,0:03:04.81,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So you still haven't regained your\Nmemory or read the logs after all?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.81,0:03:07.75,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Perhaps I'm the one who overestimated you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.42,0:03:15.56,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I intend to go to Harima Science\NGarden City and win this game.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.56,0:03:17.76,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Huh? What number are you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.76,0:03:22.33,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I didn't see any Selecao spending\Nlike they could win right now...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.33,0:03:24.30,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm Number 1.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.30,0:03:29.50,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No need to worry. I'll make it\Nso you can finish this game, too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.50,0:03:32.41,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What about it? Want to come with me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.41,0:03:34.68,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'll tell you the truth  behind that stupid phone
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.68,0:03:39.14,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and why you erased your memories, too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.99,0:03:46.65,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Takizawa, what happened?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.65,0:03:50.79,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oh, something suddenly came up.\NI'll catch up with you later.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.79,0:03:53.63,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,--Sorry.\N--Wait! Don't hang up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.53,0:04:04.21,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I know that your cell phone is special.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.21,0:04:11.20,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,When Osugi went missing, you were\Nin that hotel room with a woman.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.12,0:04:19.88,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You hadn't hung up your phone, and I\Ncould hear your whole conversation.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.52,0:04:26.69,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That woman used her phone to make\Nthose strange things happen, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.69,0:04:30.73,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Her phone that matched yours...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.73,0:04:36.37,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Takizawa, the "Selecao" are the terrorists\Nbehind Careless Monday, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.37,0:04:39.74,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Do you have anything to do with them?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.74,0:04:45.01,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah. Yeah. Hold on a second. I'll call you back.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.65,0:04:50.92,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Tell me, Takizawa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.92,0:04:52.82,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Who are you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.26,0:05:01.36,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hmm, you're right. I mean,\Neven I think it's suspicious.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.36,0:05:04.77,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But I really don't know who I am.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.60,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Believe that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.60,0:05:11.51,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Anyway, I'm about to talk with\Nsomeone who says he knows me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.51,0:05:15.38,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So will you stay on the line and listen to us?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.38,0:05:17.58,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I won't hang up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.58,0:05:22.58,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If it turns out I'm the criminal, forget about me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.58,0:05:26.05,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And I'll disappear from your life.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.05,0:05:29.79,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But...That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.77,0:05:45.24,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.24,0:05:48.87,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The only explanation is that he's\Nconnected to the NEET disappearance.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.91,0:05:58.75,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs20\fe0\b0\i0\c&Hffffff&\fnPalatino}Comment\NTell me who he is!{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.11,0:05:54.88,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Takizawa used aliases in the six cities attacked
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.88,0:05:59.25,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and gathered NEETs here\Nright after Careless Monday.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.25,0:06:02.42,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And then the NEETs vanished into thin air.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.42,0:06:05.09,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He's like the Pied Piper of Hamelin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.09,0:06:09.00,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I just hope they're not buried\Nin some building somewhere...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.00,0:06:10.33,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I don't get it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.33,0:06:13.90,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why would he need to do such a thing?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.90,0:06:15.97,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I got Micchon on the phone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.97,0:06:20.11,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She says Takky didn't get on the\Ntrain with them for some reason.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.11,0:06:22.64,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So Saki and Micchon are okay!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.64,0:06:28.58,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, that's a weird way to put it...\NAnyway, I told them to come to Toyosu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.58,0:06:30.69,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's from ltazu?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.78,0:06:33.15,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs20\fe0\b0\i0\c&Hffffff&\fnPalatino}Unable to display\Nmore\NOut of memory.{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.69,0:06:33.52,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What's with this crapload of data?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.52,0:06:35.79,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I can't open it from a cell phone!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.36,0:06:38.76,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs20\fe0\b0\i0\c&Hffffff&\fnPalatino}Receiving data{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.43,0:06:48.64,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Get in.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.47,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A helicopter?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.47,0:06:52.84,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What happened to Takky?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.64,0:06:58.38,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Aw, man, it's from Underpants.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.38,0:07:01.65,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It looks like he sent\Nsomething to the Eden server.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.65,0:07:04.68,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I can't really open it because\Nthere's too much data, though...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.29,0:07:15.36,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What are you calling yourself these days?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.36,0:07:17.80,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Akira Takizawa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.80,0:07:22.70,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"Takizawa," eh? Do you know that's an alias?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.17,0:07:27.18,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How about the fact that you\Nsent 20,000 people to Dubai?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.18,0:07:28.68,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Kind of...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.68,0:07:32.41,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Does he mean the NEET disappearance?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.41,0:07:36.18,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Some things are starting to click,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.18,0:07:42.86,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,but why did I erase my memories\Nor use aliases in the first place?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.86,0:07:48.06,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Have you heard of a firm called Ato & Company?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.06,0:07:50.06,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"Ato & Company"?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.06,0:07:55.04,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Outside, the man who got\Nyou and me mixed up in this game,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.04,0:08:00.01,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,is an old man called Saizo Ato,\Nits CEO and senior advisor.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.01,0:08:01.58,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Saizo Ato?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.58,0:08:03.85,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes. Haven't you heard of him?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.85,0:08:06.68,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He's a very well-connected\Nbusinessman who built a huge fortune
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.68,0:08:09.28,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,starting with a transport company\Nduring the reconstruction after the War.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.28,0:08:13.55,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He's one of the relics of the Showa era\Nthat some call "Japan's fixers."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.86,0:08:18.86,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What a boy of the times you are.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.86,0:08:24.20,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So why do you say Saizo Ato is Mr. Outside?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.20,0:08:28.04,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey, "Ato Saizo"... sounds like "outside"...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.04,0:08:31.57,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's just a lame pun?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.57,0:08:35.28,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There's the mocking name,\Nplus he's just about the only one
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.28,0:08:42.21,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,with the authority to get this stupid\Ngame into automated operation.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.95,0:08:47.22,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Furthermore, it's the kind of idea
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.22,0:08:49.99,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,someone with his study experience\Nin prewar Europe would like,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.99,0:08:51.83,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and he's a peerless soccer fanatic.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.83,0:08:57.57,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The name "Selecao" probably\Ncame from Brazilian soccer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.57,0:09:02.80,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It was actually quite easy to deduce\Nhis identity with those clues.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.80,0:09:05.11,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But why would an important old man like that
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.11,0:09:08.34,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,pass out ten billion yen\Nto do something so crazy?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.85,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There's no way that could fix our country!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.85,0:09:16.02,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Maybe to Mr. Outside, giving money\Nand power to a youth like you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.02,0:09:21.16,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and allowing serial murders and\Nmissile attacks by prowar believers
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.16,0:09:26.36,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,seemed like valid possible ways of saving Japan.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.36,0:09:29.36,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Saizo Ato is someone who prides himself
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.36,0:09:32.77,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,on having laid the foundation of today's Japan.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.77,0:09:34.00,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But in this age,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.00,0:09:37.61,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,he began to wonder if the nation\Nwas really on the right path.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.61,0:09:40.31,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If what he'd done was right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.31,0:09:45.81,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I think he took a good hard look at\Nthe impasse our country has come to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.81,0:09:51.52,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And then, by forcing power on the\Npeople who found favor with him,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.52,0:09:58.03,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,he sought to orchestrate another\Nmoment of dramatic change for Japan.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.03,0:10:00.36,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I still think it's crazy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.36,0:10:02.66,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I agree with you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.66,0:10:06.63,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We're the victims of his whims.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.63,0:10:13.17,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But-- though I'm not defending him--\Nhis time was running out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.17,0:10:20.05,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,By the time this game started,\Nhe'd been diagnosed with terminal cancer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.05,0:10:23.81,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And now, he must already be dead.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.26,0:10:36.66,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I wonder who this person he's talking with is?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.83,0:10:42.74,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How unfortunate that you\Ncan't punch out Mr. Outside.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.74,0:10:50.28,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, I'm not sure I could\Npunch a senior citizen anyway.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.28,0:10:54.22,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,More importantly, how are\Nyou going to win this game?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.22,0:11:00.39,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Even if the old man's dead, there's the\NSupporter, and the game's still going.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.39,0:11:06.76,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I intend to become the winner\Nby replacing Mr. Outside.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.76,0:11:09.43,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This game is ridiculous,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.43,0:11:13.57,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,but the Noblesse phone\Nsystem itself is a fine thing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.57,0:11:19.10,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,After all, it contains all of Saizo Ato's power.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.98,0:11:24.75,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You get a talented concierge\Non your phone, too, don't you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.75,0:11:27.55,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ah, you mean Juiz?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.55,0:11:30.28,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm going to make her all mine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.48,0:12:00.78,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Mononobe, is this really where Juiz works?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.59,0:12:11.29,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This is a research lab run by the Ato Foundation.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.29,0:12:14.43,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,In the years before his death,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.43,0:12:16.80,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Saizo Ato apparently spent\Nmost of his time here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.80,0:12:19.32,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You investigated that, too?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.34,0:12:29.71,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,When I realized who Outside was,\NI quit my job as a bureaucrat
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.71,0:12:34.52,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and made close connections working at\Ncompanies that had dealings with Ato.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.52,0:12:38.89,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And the other day, I assumed\Nan executive post at Ato
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.89,0:12:42.01,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and officially gained control of this place.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.80,0:12:53.80,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Including you, I've identified\Nnine of the other Selecao.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.80,0:12:57.54,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Two of those are already working with me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.54,0:12:58.71,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Huh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.71,0:13:01.37,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This is Yuki, Number 10.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.74,0:13:08.01,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He's the Selecao who\Nlaunched the eleven missiles.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.55,0:13:13.09,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Where's Tsuji?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.09,0:13:14.59,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He's waiting inside.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.59,0:13:16.18,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I see.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.86,0:13:22.86,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,--This is Juiz.\N--Juiz, prepare us some celebratory champagne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.86,0:13:25.93,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'd like you to deliver it to the control room.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.93,0:13:30.07,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's rare foryou to make\Nsuch requests, Mr. Mononobe.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.07,0:13:31.44,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Is that a no?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.44,0:13:34.51,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Not at all. You should reward\Nyourself every so often.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.51,0:13:38.08,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Noblesse oblige. I pray you\Nshall continue to be a savior.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.08,0:13:39.71,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thank you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.60,0:14:00.87,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey, Mr. Mononobe. Is there only one Juiz?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.87,0:14:04.87,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I mean, the girl who answered your\Nphone sounded the same as mine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.87,0:14:10.54,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Maybe I should feel bad about the\Nreally tough requests I've been making.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.54,0:14:15.95,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I kind of pictured a bunch of\Ngirls lined up in a huge room,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.95,0:14:20.08,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,answering our requests.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.59,0:14:23.92,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You truly are unique.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.92,0:14:27.76,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This device below our feet is Juiz.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.26,0:14:32.33,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If Ato were alive, he'd be 100 this year.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.33,0:14:37.00,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I suppose creating a great machine\Nlike this was his version of atonement.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.00,0:14:40.51,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Takizawa, now that Mr. Outside is dead,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.51,0:14:44.85,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,there's no one left but us\Nwho knows what this facility is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.85,0:14:50.92,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just as he manipulated this country\Nfrom behind the scenes to the last,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.92,0:14:56.09,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,will you join us in our plan to\Nredo Japan from the Postwar Era?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.09,0:14:57.46,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Huh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.46,0:14:59.69,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You're really going to tell him?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.69,0:15:03.30,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He is one of Japan's chosen representatives.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.30,0:15:06.50,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Whatever he may decide to do,\NI think he may at least have the right
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.50,0:15:10.47,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,to know the truth before the general populace.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.47,0:15:14.84,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What do you mean, redo it from the Postwar Era?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.84,0:15:19.95,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Tomorrow at 8:00 am, we'll launch\Nanother missile attack on Japan.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.95,0:15:23.12,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This time, it'll be sixty missiles.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.12,0:15:25.62,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Are these the people behind Careless Monday?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.62,0:15:27.11,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Shh!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.46,0:15:32.86,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This was Yuki's suggestion, but\Nbasically we'll become Japan's saviors
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.86,0:15:38.40,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,by redistributing its vested interests\Nthrough a targeted missile attack.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.20,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That makes no sense!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.20,0:15:42.67,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,More like, it's totally messed up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.67,0:15:46.74,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A "savior" doesn't attack his own country!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.74,0:15:48.34,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We're not messed up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.34,0:15:52.98,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Japan is messed up, pretending to\Nhave equality when it exploits people!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.98,0:15:55.75,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yuki claims to have received his Noblesse phone
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.75,0:16:00.02,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,right after his parents died of overwork.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.02,0:16:05.23,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There was no place left for me in this society.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.23,0:16:08.86,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It was just your typical infinite\Ncycle of non-full-time jobs.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.86,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Even after I took out a loan\Nto get official qualifications,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.86,0:16:13.87,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,my wage only went up ten yen an hour.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.87,0:16:16.27,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,When I complained, even the NEETs mocked me,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.27,0:16:20.51,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,saying it was my own responsibility\Nand I didn't work hard enough!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.51,0:16:24.21,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Those ten missiles were a message from me:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.21,0:16:28.12,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"You and the government don't\Ntake enough responsibility!"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.12,0:16:30.35,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Uh, you might be right, but...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.35,0:16:35.52,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Anyway, I'm going to make the people\Nwho mocked me feel just like I felt!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.52,0:16:38.89,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's my noblesse oblige.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.89,0:16:40.93,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And you're all right with that, Mr. Mononobe?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.93,0:16:45.43,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I take self-responsibility in all situations.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.43,0:16:48.27,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But I thought Yuki might be\Nright that the fastest way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.27,0:16:51.27,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,to downsize this country and\Nregain our global competitiveness
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.27,0:16:55.78,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,would be to first get rid of\Nthe idlers and the gerontocracy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.78,0:17:00.25,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,who keep such a tight hold\Non their vested rights.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.25,0:17:04.99,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So I decided to go along with him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.99,0:17:06.78,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What about you, then?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.82,0:17:11.89,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I already had ten billion yen,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.89,0:17:17.06,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,so all I want is to be freed from\Nthis annoying game already.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.06,0:17:19.80,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Don't interfere with me this time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.80,0:17:24.61,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Whatever, you've got the meaning\Nof "noblesse oblige" all wrong!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.61,0:17:28.44,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now I want to punch you guys out...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.44,0:17:30.68,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's probably what you said\Nbefore you lost your memories
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.68,0:17:34.85,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,when you evacuated the\Npeople from the landing sites.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.85,0:17:39.09,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You should just tell him\Nwhy he erased his memories.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.09,0:17:43.99,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If he still wants to interfere\Nwith us, I won't say anything.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.30,0:17:55.79,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You were betrayed by both those you\Nsaved and the friends who helped you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.94,0:18:03.54,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thank you for choosing the East\NJapan Railway Company today.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.38,0:18:09.12,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Wait, are these Takizawa's cell phone logs?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.12,0:18:12.38,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Number 10 has stuff written in red font.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.16,0:18:16.56,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What is this?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.56,0:18:19.13,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What are these numbers?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.19,0:18:22.05,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs20\fe0\b0\i0\c&Hffffff&\fnPalatino}Hack into the Marine SDF radars\Nto display flying objects on radar\Nand trigger a missile attack{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.13,0:18:21.56,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There's close to ten billion...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.13,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey, look at this!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.50,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs20\fe0\b0\i0\c&Hffffff&\fnPalatino}Hack Tomahawk\Nmissile Launch date:{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.13,0:18:26.36,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It says Tomahawk missile!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.34,0:18:31.57,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Could Takizawa have been\Ninvolved in Careless Monday, too?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.14,0:18:34.70,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What's that?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.88,0:18:38.87,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What is that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.72,0:18:53.39,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What? What the heck is with that naked army?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.39,0:18:55.16,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hirasawa, is that...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.16,0:18:58.67,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah, and look at how many\Nthere are-- wait, are they...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.67,0:19:01.36,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...the missing NEETs?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.28,0:19:11.04,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Run!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.28,0:19:21.28,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah, that might make me lose hope even today.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.80,0:19:35.47,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's just not fair!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.47,0:19:39.87,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's just too cruel to Takizawa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.87,0:19:45.48,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But I'm the same. I'm the same\Nas the people who betrayed him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.48,0:19:48.72,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's not true. You're different, Saki.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.72,0:19:52.72,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But when the missiles came...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.72,0:19:58.06,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...even I said, "l wish something\Neven bigger would happen"!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.26,0:20:03.26,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Was it okay to let him go?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.26,0:20:07.27,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We don't have complete\Ncommand of the system yet...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.27,0:20:12.97,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Even if he asks Juiz for something,\Nit's too late for him to do much.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.97,0:20:17.00,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There's a little over eight\Nhours to the missile launch.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.85,0:20:20.44,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ah, it's here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.95,0:20:24.62,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Bollinger, eh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.62,0:20:26.49,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This is empty.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.49,0:20:29.76,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The winner of the game\Nwas not decided this evening.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.76,0:20:32.13,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Therefore, I ask you to post pone your toast.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.13,0:20:33.93,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Noblesse oblige.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.93,0:20:36.50,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Please follow Mr. Outside's orders
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.50,0:20:40.49,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and continue the game\Nin order to become saviors.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.94,0:20:47.64,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs20\fe0\b0\i0\c&Hffffff&\fnPalatino}Selecao Activity History\N[Transfer Juiz to a secret\Nlocation]{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.87,0:20:46.87,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"Transfer Juiz to a secret location"?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.98,0:20:49.98,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Number 12 is the Supporter?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.98,0:20:52.61,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, he's Outside?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.63,0:21:15.50,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The night is a seal
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.50,0:21:22.91,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If we mix in some bewilderment, it will end
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.04,0:21:34.85,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If we're in danger of wavering,\Nlet's just abandon our reasons
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.09,0:21:42.55,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We drown in dreams again
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.90,0:21:46.70,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The future stretches on uncertainly
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.70,0:21:58.05,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I can still forgive you,\NI can still know the meaning
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.05,0:22:02.92,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The night exists to be listened to closely
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.92,0:22:09.06,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I can copy that reason, and change
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.06,0:22:19.87,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I wouldn't mind cutting off\Nthe future to know your breath
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.87,0:22:25.07,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I wouldn't mind cutting off the future